<body><h1>Creating New FogBugz Task Repository</h1>
<br><ul><li>Open Mylyn Task Repositories view. From the menu, select <span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;">Window -&gt; Show View -&gt; Other -&gt; Mylyn -&gt; Task Repositories</span><br></li><li>From the context menu, click on Add New Repository and then select FogBugz Repository<br></li></ul><ul><li>Provide
repository details namely, the FogBugz server's URL, username and
password. The Validate Settings button verifies if the credentials are
correct.</li></ul><p></p><p style="text-align: center;">



<img src="creatingNewRepo.gif" alt="Creating New Repository"></p><p></p>


